formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	We have given the certificate on the basis of books of accounts certified by the promoter of the project.
2.	The Annexure of Form 3 Excel Sheet i.e. Unit wise detail of carpet area and estimated selling price of the project & KYC details are given after certified and confirmed by the project head of the project.
3.	In some cases, the promoter has made directly sale deed instead of Agreement for sale and hence instead of date of agreement for sale, we have written the date of registration of sale deed while giving this certificate. 
4.	The Encumbrance detail and Date of Agreement for Sale & Encumbrance Status are given after confirmed and certified by the Promoter of the Partnership Firm
5.	The Encumbrance State of the unit is given after certified by the promoter of the project, No NOC is produced by the promoter while giving this certificate.
6.	The Promoter has taken addition Loan amount of Rs.1,98,00,000/- due to COVID-19 crises and hence this amount is given in the Loan Details while giving this certificate
